case class OshkoshWeather(Year: String, 
Month: String, 
Day: String, 
TimeCST: String,
TemperatureF: Integer, 
DewPointF: Integer, 
Humidity: Integer, 
SeaLevelPressure: Double, 
VisibilityMPH: Double, 
WindDirection: String, 
windSpeedMPH: Double, 
gustspeedmph: Double, 
precipitationIn: String, 
events: String, 
conditions: String, 
winddirdegrees: Integer)

val Oshkosh = spark.read.format("csv").option("header", true).option("inferSchema", true).load("/user/maria_dev/final/Oshkosh/OshkoshWeather.csv")
Oshkosh.createOrReplaceTempView("OshkoshWeather")

paragraphs.text: spark.sqlContext.sql("select 'oshkosh' as city, to_timestamp(concat(string(oshkoshstart.year), '-', string(oshkoshstart.month), '-', string(oshkoshstart.day), ' ', oshkoshstart.timeCST), 'yyyy-m-d hh:mm a') oshkoshstarttime, to_timestamp(concat(string(oshkoshend.year), '-', string(oshkoshend.month), '-', string(oshkoshend.day), ' ', oshkoshend.timeCST), 'yyyy-m-d hh:mm a') oshkoshendtime, oshkoshstart.TemperatureF, oshkoshend.TemperatureF, ABS(oshkoshstart.TemperatureF - oshkoshend.TemperatureF) as TempShift  from oshkoshweather oshkoshstart join oshkoshweather oshkoshend on  to_timestamp(concat(string(oshkoshend.year), '-', string(oshkoshend.month), '-', string(oshkoshend.day), ' ', oshkoshend.timeCST), 'yyyy-m-d hh:mm a') between to_timestamp(concat(string(oshkoshstart.year), '-', string(oshkoshstart.month), '-', string(oshkoshstart.day), ' ', oshkoshstart.timeCST), 'yyyy-m-d hh:mm a') and DATE_ADD(to_timestamp(concat(string(oshkoshstart.year), '-', string(oshkoshstart.month), '-', string(oshkoshstart.day), ' ', oshkoshstart.timeCST), 'yyyy-m-d hh:mm a'), 1) where oshkoshstart.temperatureF != -9999 and oshkoshend.temperatureF != -9999 and  oshkoshstart.temperatureF != oshkoshend.temperatureF and oshkoshstart.TimeCST != 'No daily or hourly history data available' and oshkoshend.timeCST != 'No daily or hourly history data available' order by 6 desc").show()
